OL,4,C- what's going on?
OL,6,FA bitter row has broken out at the
OL,7,Fheart of Reform UK, as party leader
OL,8,FNigel Farage and Reform MP Rupert Lowe
OL,9,Fclash over claims about Lowe's
OL,10,Fbehaviour.
OL,12,FThe public spat has been played out in
OL,13,Fsocial media posts and newspaper
OL,14,Fopinion pages, as the two men battle
OL,15,Fto dispute the others' claims.
OL,17,FAs the party continues to surge in the
OL,18,Fpolls, this dispute threatens to
OL,19,Fderail its recent successes.
