OL,6,FWhat does Reform claim Rupert Lowe has
OL,7,Fdone?
OL,9,FThe day after Lowe's initial comments
OL,10,Fwere published in the Daily Mail,
OL,11,FReform announced they had suspended
OL,12,Fhim over allegations of bullying and
OL,13,Fthreatening violence.
OL,15,FThe party released a statement, saying
OL,16,Fit had received evidence of "serious
OL,17,Fbullying" and "derogatory" remarks
OL,18,Fmade about women in Lowe's offices,
OL,19,Fwith two separate employees said to
OL,20,Fhave made allegations.
