OL,6,FLowe is most well-known for being the
OL,7,Fchairman of Southampton Football Club
OL,8,Fbetween 1996-2006, and again from 2008-
OL,9,F2009.
OL,11,FThe multi-millionaire businessman
OL,12,Ffounded care home provider Secure
OL,13,FRetirements, and later served as a
OL,14,FBrexit Party MEP following the 2019
OL,15,FEuropean elections.
OL,17,FIn the 2019 general election he was
OL,18,Fdue to stand as a Brexit Party
OL,19,Fcandidate, but pulled out at the last
OL,20,Fminute. He also stood in the Kingswood
OL,21,Fby-election in February 2024.
